{"tid":573772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴/絲有玩Space Engineers","createTime":"2018-02-26T18:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T00:19:16.000Z","uid":121100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"240aa0af75ae7c99b685a84a859e56d2ba0834f7","tid":573772,"uid":121100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T18:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/022736_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F022736_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=74acc7a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSpace Engineers係一隻喺Steam平台推出嘅多人sandbox建築遊戲，有分Creative同Survival mode.當中加入左生存、戰鬥等嘅元素。<br />\n<br />\n喺game入面，玩家可以盡情發揮自己嘅創意，天馬行空。可以砌車、飛機、太空飛船、甚至係宇宙戰艦。只要你諗到，就可以喺game入面砌出黎。<br />\n<br />\n奉上小弟劣作-「卡拉之杖」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/023328_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F023328_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=0819538b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/023335_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F023335_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7af395ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/023339_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F023339_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=413747c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/023345_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F023345_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e